---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Blog | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Security insights, tips, and news from Sheepdog Cyber Defense. Learn about penetration testing, cybersecurity best practices, and how to protect your Texas business." showMatrix={true}>
  <section>
    <h1>Security Blog</h1>
    <p class="lead">Insights on penetration testing, cybersecurity, and protecting your business.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="posts">
    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/5-signs-your-business-needs-pentest.html">5 Signs Your Business Needs a Penetration Test</a></h2>
      <p>Not sure if your business needs penetration testing? Here are 5 clear signs that indicate it's time to test your security posture.</p>
      <a href="/blog/5-signs-your-business-needs-pentest.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/why-choose-local-security-consultant.html">Why Choose a Local Security Consultant?</a></h2>
      <p>Working with a local penetration testing company in Bulverde, Spring Branch, or San Antonio offers real advantages. Learn why local matters for your business security.</p>
      <a href="/blog/why-choose-local-security-consultant.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/common-vulnerabilities-small-business.html">Common Vulnerabilities in Small Business Networks</a></h2>
      <p>Small businesses face real security threats. Learn about the most common vulnerabilities we find in Texas small business networks and how to address them.</p>
      <a href="/blog/common-vulnerabilities-small-business.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/red-teaming-vs-pentesting.html">Red Teaming vs Penetration Testing</a></h2>
      <p>What's the difference between red teaming and penetration testing? Learn which approach is right for your organization.</p>
      <a href="/blog/red-teaming-vs-pentesting.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/how-often-should-you-pentest.html">How Often Should You Conduct Security Assessments?</a></h2>
      <p>Annual testing isn't always enough. Learn how often you should conduct penetration tests and what events should trigger additional assessments.</p>
      <a href="/blog/how-often-should-you-pentest.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/what-is-penetration-testing.html">What is Penetration Testing?</a></h2>
      <p>Learn what penetration testing is and why your Texas business needs it. Discover how ethical hackers identify vulnerabilities before cybercriminals do.</p>
      <a href="/blog/what-is-penetration-testing.html" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .posts { display: grid; gap: 2rem; }
  article { background: var(--bg-alt); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  article h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  article h2 a { color: var(--text); }
  article h2 a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  article p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .read-more { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
</style>
